extendedInfo.description: Deal Twin Cities brings you savings from 50-90% off the best stuff to do, see, eat and buy. Download the Deal Twin Cities app to get fresh deals sent directly to your Android Phone when they become available. Whether you are looking for a new restaurant, a great salon, a concert event or a local attraction, check out Deal Twin Cities for great savings! With the Deal Twin Cities app you can: - Buy and redeem your Deal Twin Cities voucher directly from your phone - Yes, you can save ink! - Browse and Search local and national deals - View the business details including locations - Track your purchased Deal Twin Cities vouchers, including gifts given and/or received - Update your profile settings, view your site credit bucks, add/remove subscriptions
